every section in the story has to be stored in an object
each choice has to be stored in array(s) that are apart of the main story object

all adventyre mechanics should use objects and methods

use classes for items,characters, npc's... ect

maintain a record or list of the choices the user makes and display it at the end of the game

NOT use the  prompt, alert, or confirm methods to gather or display information. 

Perform all operations within functions. Only bindings should be at the Global level.